<C>__{duena}
<D>__{"i should be judged as a seaman who by divine will discovered a new world, and thereby placed it under the sovereignty of your majesties. i humbly beseech your majesties that if it pleases god to remove me hence, you will help the name of columbus to be remembered with honor... weep for me, whoever has charity, truth and justice."}
